elements.name: Selecting the product correctly and seeing its definition

steps.name: the user is on the main page
the user clicks on burger menu for all products
the user clicks "Electronics, Computers & Office" on the main page
the user clicks the "TV & Home Theatre" on the main page
the user is on the categorised product page with "Amazon.ca: Televisions & Video: Electronics: Accessories, Projectors, AV Receivers & Amplifiers, Televisions & More"

steps.name: the user clicks the "Televisions" which is under the "Electronics" on the categorised product page
the user is on the product page with "Amazon.ca: Televisions - Televisions & Video: Electronics"
the user selects price preference from "Price: High to Low" on the result page
the user clicks the second highest priced product on the results page
